document_data.name: Poison Sea
document_data.mainbody: The '''Poison Sea''' was an aquifer located beneath the [[Howling Mountains]] in [[Relmaur]], [[Laerakond]].
document_data.Inhabitants: A tribe of [[genasi]] known as the [[Saqr]] lived on an island made of crystal located in the center of the aquifer.
